data.description:
4 Bedroom, 2 1/2 Bathroom Townhouse in  Briarheath development in Manalapan.  Three large bedrooms and two full bathrooms on the top floor with an additional Fourth bedroom on the Lower level which walks out to a beautiful deck for outdoor entertainment.  Hard wood floors on the main level.  This Home features a newer Furnace, HVAC and Hot Water Heater.  Briarheath is located close to shopping, restaurants and commuting to NYC.  Bus stop is on the corner of Lone Star Ln and Wilson. 

Home is vacant and easy to show.
